OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776791154
OL,3,CTeenage boy charged with arson over
OL,4,Csynagogue attack in Harrow
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith arson after an attack on a
OL,8,Fsynagogue in north-west London.
OL,10,FThe teenager, a British national from
OL,11,FBrent, north-west London, who has not
OL,12,Fbeen named because of his age, is due
OL,13,Fto appear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt on Tuesday.
OL,16,FHe is accused of arson not endangering
OL,17,Flife.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
