OL,3,CTeenage boy charged with arson over
OL,4,Csynagogue attack in Harrow
OL,6,FFootage was posted online of a figure
OL,7,Fin dark clothing setting light to a
OL,8,Fbottle of liquid and throwing it
OL,9,Fthrough a window at Kenton United
OL,10,FSynagogue in Harrow late on Saturday.
OL,12,FJewish charity the Community Security
OL,13,FTrust said minor smoke damage to an
OL,14,Finternal room was caused but there
OL,15,Fwere no injuries or significant
OL,16,Fstructural damage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
