CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776791154
OL,3,CTeenage boy charged with arson over
OL,4,Csynagogue attack in Harrow
OL,6,FA 19-year-old man who was also
OL,7,Farrested after the attack has been
OL,8,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,9,Finquiries, the Metropolitan Police
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe attack was the latest in a string
OL,13,Fof separate incidents that have
OL,14,Ftargeted Jewish sites in London.
OL,16,FFour Jewish community ambulances were
OL,17,Fdestroyed in an arson attack in
OL,18,FGolders Green on March 23, and there
OL,19,Fhave been further attacks at a
OL,20,Fsynagogue in Finchley and a former
OL,21,FJewish charity building in Hendon.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
