PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776791154
OL,3,CTeenage boy charged with arson over
OL,4,Csynagogue attack in Harrow
OL,6,FAnother incident saw a drone flown
OL,7,Fnear the Israeli embassy in London.
OL,9,FA group that calls itself Harakat
OL,10,FAshab al-Yamin al-Islamia, the Islamic
OL,11,FMovement of the Companions of the
OL,12,FRight, that is suspected to be Iran-
OL,13,Fbacked, has claimed responsibility for
OL,14,Fmost of the incidents, along with
OL,15,Fother attacks in Europe, since March 9.
